edu.washington.cs.dm.jeremyc.netflix
Class MemStore

java.lang.Object
  edu.washington.cs.dm.jeremyc.netflix.MemStore

public class MemStore
extends java.lang.Object

The in-memory store of the training data. Consists of two maps, one from MovieID to all Ratings for that movie and one from UserID to all ratings by that user.

Nested Class Summary
(package private) static class MemStore.Rating
          An ID rating pair.
(package private) static class MemStore.Ratings
          A simple wrapper around List<Rating> that caches the average of the rating values, and provides an init() method, called after the list is filled, to ensure the Rating list is sorted by ID and the average computed.
